#: ../../chapter-14.rst:5
msgid ""
"py4web comes with a Grid object providing grid and CRUD (create, update "
"and delete) capabilities. This allows you to quickly and safely provide "
"an interface to your data. Since it's also highly customizable, it's the "
"corner stone of most py4web's applications."
