#: ../../chapter-14.rst:389
msgid "Grid mode parameter (path replacement)"
msgstr "Grid 模式参数（路径替换）"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:391
msgid ""
"The `Grid` object uses a `mode` variable, which is passed via the "
"`request.query` object in py4web. This variable determines what kind of "
"page or form the grid will render. Possible values for `mode` are:"
msgstr ""
"`Grid` 对象使用一个 `mode` 变量，该变量通过 py4web 中的 `request.query` 对象传递。此变量决定 grid "
"将呈现什么类型的页面或表单。 `mode` 的可能值有："

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:393
msgid ""
"`select`: Shows the main grid listing all records (default if not "
"specified)."
msgstr "`select`: 显示列出所有记录的主表（如果未指定，则默认）。"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:394
msgid "`new`: Shows a form to create a new record."
msgstr "`new`: 显示一个表单以创建新记录。"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:395
msgid "`details`: Shows a read-only form with details of a single record."
msgstr "`details`: 显示一个只读表单，其中包含单个记录的详细信息。"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:396
msgid "`edit`: Shows a form to edit an existing record."
msgstr "`edit`: 显示一个表单以编辑现有记录。"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:397
msgid "`delete`: Shows a confirmation form to delete a record."
msgstr "`delete`: 显示删除记录的确认表单。"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:399
msgid ""
"The grid automatically parses the `mode` from the URL query parameters. "
"For example, if you visit `/myapp/mygrid?mode=edit&id=5`, the grid will "
"render the edit form for the record with ID 5. If no `mode` is specified,"
" the grid defaults to `select` and shows the main table view."
msgstr ""
"grid 会自动从 URL 查询参数中解析 `mode` 。例如，如果您访问 `/myapp/mygrid?mode=edit&id=5` "
"，grid 将呈现 id 为 5 的记录的编辑表单。如果未指定 `mode` ，则 grid 默认使用 `select` 模式并显示主表视图。"

#: ../../chapter-14.rst:401
msgid ""
"If you want to customize navigation or actions, you can generate links or"
" buttons that set the desired `mode` and `id` in the query string."
msgstr "如果要自定义导航或操作，可以生成链接或按钮，在查询字符串中设置所需的模式和 id 。"

